Sequoia : macOS 15 

 

softwareupdate --fetch-full-installer version-number 

softwareupdate --list-full-installer version-number 

 

softwareupdate --fetch-full-installer --full-installer-version 15.4 

hdiutil create -o /tmp/Sequoia -size 17000m -volname Sequoia -layout SPUD -fs HFS+J 

hdiutil attach /tmp/Sequoia.dmg -noverify -mountpoint /Volumes/Sequoia 

sudo /Applications/Install\ macOS\ Sequoia.app/Contents/Resources/createinstallmedia --volume /Volumes/Sequoia --nointeraction 

hdiutil detach -force /volumes/Install\ macOS\ Sequoia/ 

 

Convert DMG to ISO 

hdiutil convert /tmp/Sequoia.dmg -format UDTO -o /tmp/Sequoia.cdr 

mv /tmp/Sequoia.cdr /tmp/macos-15.4.iso 
